{
  "stem": "11998.6",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Everywhere where there was a hiding place, there were already two or three guys hiding in that place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so we tried-- we stayed back as far as we could in-- in the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then, finally, they cleaned the camp out, and they got us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I came to the commandant and I said-- I said, I can't go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I'm too weak to walk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I says, rather than die on the-- on the way, I'm going to die here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And please let me stay.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my-- I said, can my father stay too?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says-- he looked at him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a big boned man, so he-- when he was a skeleton, he looked big, with big cheekbone.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so he says, no, he has to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I said, well, then I'm going to go with him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he sort of half carried, half dragged me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we went and turned around to-- walked away from him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he changed his mind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He called us back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He says, you can both stay.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that train went out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the next night, it was bombed by the Americans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the prisoners started running.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the soldiers were-- the Nazis were shooting everybody who was getting off the train.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I met somebody in Toronto many years later that was on the train, that ran away, who had successfully ran away off the train, hid in a farmer's barn for three days, and survived the war.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "With us, we stayed in the barracks, in the infirmary.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
